# GoogleHubs Platform - Master AI Prompt
## Complete Platform Documentation for AI Replication

---

## PLATFORM OVERVIEW

**GoogleHubs** is an all-in-one CRM, AI Powered platform, personal AI Assistant, and business AI Assistant, AI automation workflows designed to replace 15-18 different software tools for service professionals, businesses, and agencies to save time, improve process, increase productivity, and make more money. Meet Helix, your all in one personal and business management center that combines CRM, marketing, campaigns, automation, AI-powered workflows, emergency services integration, smart home control, and industry-specific features into a single unified platform.

HELIX is the ultimate marketing tool. generate AI powered articles, books, manuscripts, children's books and more. Convert you book or script to a movie and sell tickets to the premiere.

**Core Value Proposition:**
- Replace GoHighLevel, Salesforce, ServiceTitan, and 15-18 other tools
- Save $2500-12,000/month in software costs
- Industry-specific features for doctors, plumbers, lawyers, real estate, insurance, and 20+ industries
- AI automation that saves 10-30 hours per week
- Emergency Services Platform (EPS) with 911 integration
- Built-in affiliate program with 20-30% commissions

**Target Users:**
- Healthcare professionals (doctors, dentists, chiropractors, therapists, veterinarians)
- Home service providers (plumbers, electricians, HVAC, contractors, landscapers)
- Professional services (lawyers, accountants, real estate agents, insurance agents, consultants)
- Emergency services (police, fire, EMS, security companies)
- Automotive (dealerships, repair shops, detailing, towing)
- Hospitality (hotels, resorts, bed & breakfasts)
- Mortgage lenders, car rental companies, airlines
- Everyday person who wants to make life easier

---

## TECHNOLOGY STACK

### Frontend
- **Framework:** React 18.x with React Router v6
- **UI Library:** Custom component library built on Radix UI primitives
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 3.x with custom design system
- **State Management:** React Context API (AuthContext, ThemeContext)
- **Charts:** Recharts for analytics visualization
- **Forms:** Custom form components with validation
- **Icons:** Lucide React icon library
- **HTTP Client:** Axios
- **Notifications:** Sonner toast notifications
- **WebSockets:** Native WebSocket API for real-time updates

### Backend
- **Framework:** FastAPI (Python 3.11+)
- **Database:** MongoDB with Motor (async driver)
- **Authentication:** JWT tokens with httpOnly cookies
- **Security:** bcrypt for password hashing, CORS middleware
- **File Storage:** Local storage with plans for S3 integration
- **Real-time:** WebSocket connections for notifications
- **Background Tasks:** FastAPI BackgroundTasks
- **Process Management:** Supervisor for service orchestration

### Infrastructure
- **Deployment:** Kubernetes cluster
- **Container:** Docker
- **Reverse Proxy:** Nginx with ingress rules
- **Environment:** .env files for configuration
- **Ports:** 
  - Frontend: 3000 (internal)
  - Backend: 8001 (internal, mapped via /api prefix)
  - MongoDB: 27017

### External Integrations
- **Stripe:** Payment processing and billing
- **Twilio:** SMS and voice communication
- ** Telnyx:** SMS and voice communication
- **GoBrunch:** Virtual event and webinar platform
- **Google Workspace:** Calendar, Sheets, Drive, Meet integration, docs, gmail, tasks, slides
- **Google AI Studio**
- **Google NotebookLM**
- **Google Opal**
- **OpenAI/Anthropic/Gemini:** AI models via integrations library
- **Emergency Services:** 911 integration APIs
- **Pharmacy APIs:** Walgreens, CVS for prescription automation
- **Insurance APIs:** Verification and claims processing

