### 9. SMART HOME & IOT CONTROL
**Purpose:** Control smart home devices and create automation scenes

**Features:**
- **Helix Voice Assistant:** "Helix" wake word for voice commands
- **Device Integration:** SmartThings, Philips Hue, Nest, Ring, August, Ecobee
- **Scene Automation:** Custom scenes (Good Morning, Good Night, Away, Movie Time)
- **Geofencing:** Trigger actions based on location (arrive home = unlock door)
- **Presence Detection:** Know who's home via phone presence
- **Sun Times Automation:** Adjust lights/thermostats based on sunrise/sunset
- **Security Integration:** Arm/disarm systems, view cameras, lock/unlock doors
- **Energy Monitoring:** Track usage and optimize for savings
- **Device Rooms:** Organize devices by physical room
- **Voice Training:** Customize voice commands and responses

**Smart Home Workflows:**
- **Morning Routine:** Alarm → lights gradually brighten → coffee maker starts → news briefing
- **Leaving Home:** Lock doors → arm security → set thermostat to away → close garage
- **Movie Time:** Dim lights → close blinds → turn on TV → mute phones
- **Bedtime:** Lock all doors → arm security → turn off lights → set thermostat to night mode

**API Endpoints:**
- GET /api/home/devices - List all connected devices
- POST /api/home/devices/{id}/control - Control device state
- GET /api/home/scenes - List automation scenes
- POST /api/home/scenes - Create new scene
- POST /api/home/scenes/{id}/execute - Trigger scene
- GET /api/home/geofences - List geofence rules
- POST /api/home/presence - Update presence status

