  - Basic: $49/month
  - Starter: $99/month
  - Growth: $199/month
  - Professional: $299/month (popular for doctors, professionals)
  - Business: $399/month
  - Enterprise: $499/month (custom pricing available)
- **Credit System:** Purchase credits for SMS, emails, AI tokens
- **Wallet Management:** Track balance, auto-reload, low balance alerts
- **Invoice Generation:** Auto-create invoices with line items
- **Payment Methods:** Credit card, ACH, PayPal integration
- **Recurring Billing:** Automatic monthly/annual charges
- **Usage Tracking:** Monitor SMS, voice minutes, AI calls, storage
- **Overage Billing:** Charge for usage above plan limits
- **Agency White-Label:** Resell platform with custom branding

**Subscription Tiers Feature Matrix:**
