|---------|------|-------|---------|--------|-----|----------|------------|
| Leads | 100 | 500 | 2,000 | 10,000 | Unlimited | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| Users | 1 | 1 | 2 | 5 | 10 | 25 | Unlimited |
| SMS/month | 100 | 500 | 2,000 | 5,000 | 10,000 | 25,000 | Custom |
| Email/month | 1,000 | 5,000 | 20,000 | 50,000 | Unlimited | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| AI Tokens/month | 10,000 | 50,000 | 200,000 | 500,000 | 1M | 5M | Custom |
| Storage | 1GB | 10GB | 50GB | 200GB | 500GB | 1TB | Custom |
| Emergency Services | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| Health Monitoring | - | - | - | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| Smart Home | - | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| API Access | - | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| White-Label | - | - | - | - | - | ✓ | ✓ |
| Dedicated Support | - | - | - | - | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |

**API Endpoints:**
- GET /api/billing/plans - List all subscription plans
