- Pricing not public, estimated $300-500/month
- Additional fees: 2-3% of revenue processed
- Implementation: $5,000-10,000 one-time
- Training: $1,000-3,000

**Kareo / athenahealth:**
- Kareo: $160/provider/month (medical billing only)
- athenahealth: $140-500/provider/month (EHR + billing)
- Setup fees: $1,000-5,000

**GoogleHubs Competitive Advantage:**
- 50-80% cheaper than Salesforce
- More features than GoHighLevel at similar price
- No per-user fees (flat rate per account)
- No revenue-based fees
- No setup/implementation fees
- Includes emergency services, health monitoring, smart home
- 14-day free trial, no credit card required
- 30-day money-back guarantee

