## DEPLOYMENT & OPERATIONS

### Environment Variables (.env files)

**Backend .env:**
```
MONGO_URL=mongodb://localhost:27017
DB_NAME=googlehubs
JWT_SECRET=googlehubs_jwt_secret_key_2025
PLATFORM_SUPER_ADMIN_EMAIL=tjberkley@hobbsai.com

# Stripe
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_xxxxx
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_xxxxx

# Twilio
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=ACxxxxx
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=xxxxx
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+15551234567

# GoBrunch
GOBRUNCH_USER_KEY=xxxxx
GOBRUNCH_PASSWORD_KEY=xxxxx

# Emergent Integrations (for OpenAI, Gemini, Claude)
EMERGENT_LLM_KEY=xxxxx
```

**Frontend .env:**
```
REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL=https://your-domain.com
REACT_APP_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_xxxxx
```

### Supervisor Configuration
- Backend: Python/FastAPI on port 8001
- Frontend: React dev server on port 3000 (or build served by Nginx)
- MongoDB: Port 27017
- Auto-restart on failure
- Log rotation: 10MB max, 5 backups

### Kubernetes Ingress Rules
- All /api/* routes → Backend (port 8001)
- All other routes → Frontend (port 3000)
- SSL/TLS termination at ingress
- CORS handled by backend middleware

### Monitoring & Logging
- Backend logs: /var/log/supervisor/backend.*.log
- Frontend logs: Browser console + /var/log/supervisor/frontend.*.log
- Error tracking: Sentry integration (future)
- Uptime monitoring: UptimeRobot or Pingdom (future)
- Analytics: Google Analytics + internal tracking

